213
00:16:57,020 --> 00:17:01,590
Ak nepôjdete na cvičenie,
potom tu pre vás nie je žiadne mäso.

214
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:06,390
Eun Bi! To som ja.

215
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,780
Otvor dvere!

216
00:17:12,630 --> 00:17:14,590
