01:00:26,090 --> 01:00:27,610
Vrátim sa len keď si to poriadne premyslím.

811
01:00:27,645 --> 01:00:28,670
Jae Yi...

812
01:00:29,050 --> 01:00:31,630
Minulú noc si tu bola s Hong Jae Yim?

813
01:00:32,350 --> 01:00:33,960
Milujem Hong Jae Yiho.

